keyValuePair.Value: Are you happy you've been promoted with games to spare?
Are you happy you've been promoted with games to spare?
It's a great achievement, securing promotion with games to spare in a league as competitive as this one. What will this mean for the club and its future?
It's a great achievement, securing promotion with games to spare in a league as competitive as this one. What will this mean for the club and its future?
The boys have exceeded expectations.
We always thought we'd be in the running for promotion, but to go up with games to spare says it all about this group of players. They've been outstanding from day one and deserve this success.
This has to be just the start for this team.
Promotion takes the club back to where it belongs. And I'm glad we've done it in style. But next season will be a real challenge. We have to make sure we're ready for it when the time comes.
It's all eyes on next season now.
We're happy we've given the fans something to celebrate. But all our focus is on next season already. We know we'll have to face much stronger teams in the division above.
Are your boys losing their nerve?
Promotion's within your grasp now. You could even have clinched it today but the team wasn't at its best. Are you still confident they'll get there in the end?
We'll all take a deep breath!
Today was just one of those days. I'm sure we'll get there. We just need to make sure we go into our next game 100% switched on.
Today was just one of those days. I'm sure we'll get there. We just need to make sure we go into our next game 100% switched on.
I hope we're not struggling with the pressure.
I expected us to do it today but we looked nervous and disjointed. This is when it counts. I need every player to be mentally strong. We have to do it!
I'm not going to speculate.
Today wasn't our best day, but I'm not here to speculate about why that was. I'm sure we'll be fine. This is a mature group of players. I'm confident they'll get the job done.
Today wasn't our best day, but I'm not here to speculate about why that was. I'm sure we'll be fine. This is a mature group of players. I'm confident they'll get the job done.
Are you nervous about your promotion prospects?
It was a real chance to seal promotion today but you couldn't get the result you needed. Are you worried that the problems we saw today might make it difficult for your team now?
We'll get there, I'm sure.
I'm not going to read too much into what happened today. Every team has games when things don't go their way. We'll prepare for the next match now and make sure we're back to our best.
I'm not going to read too much into what happened today. Every team has games when things don't go their way. We'll prepare for the next match now and make sure we're back to our best.
We weren't at our best, that's for sure.
It's unfortunate the team's run into poor form at such a vital moment. I thought we'd do it today. We'll just have to make sure we're switched on in our next game and get the job done.
I won't put extra pressure on the boys.
I won't put extra pressure on the boys.
We didn't win today but that doesn't suddenly make us a bad team. I believe in these players and I'm sure they can get us over the line in our next game.
We didn't win today but that doesn't suddenly make us a bad team. I believe in these players and I'm sure they can get us over the line in our next game.
Are you relieved to have secured promotion already?
Are you relieved to have secured promotion already?
It's been an excellent season for you. And you've avoided any last-minute nerves by confirming promotion with games still left to play. You must be very happy with your team?
It's been an excellent season for you. And you've avoided any last-minute nerves by confirming promotion with games still left to play. You must be very happy with your team?
The boys have been relentless.
Great performance today and I'm sure our fans are delighted we're going up. All the credit goes to the players. They've driven themselves on in every game all season. This is their reward.
We have to build on this achievement.
We're the best team in the division and we've confirmed that today. I hope that motivates us to push ourselves harder. Life will be challenging for all of us next season.
Now's the time to prepare ourselves.
I think we've known for a while that we'd be going up. So we're already preparing for next season. There will be stronger teams waiting for us in the division above, that's for sure.
You won't be stopped now, will you?
Games still to play and only one point needed to secure promotion. Your team's in a very strong position. Nobody's going to be able to stop you now, are they?
The players have got us here.
The team's where it deserves to be. The boys have been consistent all season and that's why we're in such a good position going into the last few games. I think we'll be promoted soon.
This team only plays one way.
We're in a very strong position, of course, but that won't affect preparations for our next game. This team goes out to win every match. You'll never see us playing for draws.
We'll be professional.
We're in a great position and I'm optimistic about our chances. But today? All I can say is we'll give %1s the respect they deserve, and be as professional as we can be going into the game.
Will promotion be tied up today?
A great season for the club, Mr %1s. You're just one win away from sealing promotion. Is this next game the one in which your boys will pick up the points that you need?

We're almost there.
The boys have gone about their work in such a professional way all season. I expect the same in this next game. If we're at our best, that should be enough to see us promoted.

The boys can't wait for the game.

We're very close but I don't think the players are feeling any pressure. I trust them to stay focused on the game and not be distracted by the prize. We can win and that will see us promoted.

We have games still to play.

I'm not going to put pressure on the players by making the whole season depend on this next game. Let's keep calm. We have other games still to play. Other opportunities. All we want is to make sure of promotion.
